to run script in crontab use this command
crontab -e
then add this line to file
*/1 * * * * SCRIPT_PATH/section_C.sh FOLDER_PATH BACKUP_PATH

Where first argument is path to script
SCRIPT_PATH/section_C.sh

Second and third is source directory and backup directory
FOLDER_PATH
BACKUP_PATH

To save all changes in directory to file run script 
directory_logging.sh FOLDER_PATH

where path is a directory for listening
